<plot>Paul is a young writer headed to Los Angeles. He's spending his last hours before departure in a quiet airport hotel. When circumstances force him out of his room he meets an interesting group of fellow travelers. There's James, the charmingly naive actor. Mary, the beauty James is trying to woo. Harry, the outspoken and obnoxious filmmaker. Then there's James' mysterious younger sister Rita. What starts as a night of conversation soon leads to a growing friendship. But everyone has to leave at some point, right?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?426002</url></doc>
